message.body: It was really good to see you today. I hope you had a good time at the Barnes. Hopefully I can make it to NYC next week and see the cloisters. Take care.
######so good to see you. The Barnes was pretty amazing. You should definitely go. Hope to see you soon even if you don't come up next weekend. Miss you!
I'm glad you enjoyed it. I will try to make a trip up soon even if I can't make it next week. I've missed seeing you too. Have a safe trip back to ny and stay in touch :)
